                                <title type="desc">Regula salvatoris (The Birgittine Rule, the third-person version)</title>
                                <rubric>Incipit regula sancti Saluatoris beate Birgitte diuinitus reuelata De humilitate Castitate et paupertate Capitulum primum</rubric>
                                <incipit>PRIncipium itaque huius <sic>relligionis</sic> et salutis</incipit>
                                <explicit>et cogitent in cordibus suis quod terra sunt et in terram reuertentur</explicit>
                                <finalRubric>Finit Regula sancti Saluatoris</finalRubric>
                                <note>The text corresponds to Eklund's sigma version.</note>
                                <bibl>
                                    <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107122">Eklund (1975)</title>
